OL,4,CPM needs independent standards adviser
OL,5,C- Labour
OL,6, Labour has urged the PM to appoint a
OL,7, fully "independent" figure to oversee
OL,8, ministers' conduct, including his own.
OL,10,FLord Geidt - announced on Wednesday as
OL,11,FBoris Johnson's new standards adviser -
OL,12,Fwill look into the funding of the
OL,13,Frecent Downing Street flat renovations.
OL,15,FLabour leader Sir Keir Starmer said it
OL,16,Fwas wrong that Lord Geidt needed to get
OL,17,Fthe PM's permission before carrying out
OL,18,Fthis and other inquiries.
OL,20,FBut No 10 said "successive" advisers
OL,21,Fhad been taken on under these terms.
